{
  "id": "8.5-2",
  "title": "Act 2: The First Game",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch8_5_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} discovered it first.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She drew a grid on the ground with stones. Two people took turns placing stones in the grid, and the first to form a line won. She explained the rules, then looked toward {{characters.alea.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Do you know how? This one or any other? Is there something you usually play?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} was silent for a moment. That silence made {{characters.lyra.name}} realize she'd asked a question she wasn't prepared for.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "No. I don't know how to play. I've never learned any games. There wasn't time for things like that on the lower decks.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} watched her, let that sentence settle. She didn't let the weight show on her face.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Then I'll teach you. Start with this one—it's the simplest.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She explained the rules again, more slowly this time, more clearly. When she finished, she placed a handful of small stones in front of {{characters.alea.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Your turn first.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} looked down at the grid, watched for a moment, then placed a stone.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She lost that round quickly. After {{characters.lyra.name}} formed a line, {{characters.alea.name}} looked at the result without speaking, cleared the stones, and reset them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She lost again, this time taking longer. On the third move, she sensed {{characters.lyra.name}}'s intention and tried to block, but blocked in the wrong direction.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} began to notice something in the process. {{characters.alea.name}} watched every game not for the result, but for each move. She watched where {{characters.lyra.name}} placed her stone at each critical moment, studied the logic behind that choice. She was dismantling that logic, then trying again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her learning method was the same as how she spoke. No questions, no explanations, just watching, thinking, doing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Then {{characters.lyra.name}} noticed her expression.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Usually there was a layer to her face, thin but present. Now that layer had thinned. When she stared at the grid, analyzing the next move, that layer was nearly gone.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Revealed was a different expression. Focused, clear, intent. That expression made her look smaller, not in body size, but in another way.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} watched that expression, and her stone slipped from her hand.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She lost.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "You won.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} looked at the completed line, fell silent for a moment. Her expression didn't change, but something flickered in her eyes, very subtle, very brief.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Don't you want to celebrate?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} laughed and cleared the stones. Again. She was serious this time, no distractions. She won that round, then {{characters.alea.name}} won the next, then they tied.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "I'm joining.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "This game is for two people.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "Then I'll wait.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "We could create a three-person version.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "I don't know the three-person version.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "That's fine, I'll figure it out.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "Think out loud and explain while I sit down.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} watched the two of them without speaking. But she moved her stones aside slightly, creating space.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "That space was just enough for {{characters.elias.name}} to sit in.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1200,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}